{"tid":158670,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKBN]HKBN真係好識做生意","createTime":"2017-03-16T12:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T05:25:24.000Z","uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"634a17776ec9847a81d67e542aea44b4e0682d51","tid":158670,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"話說我前年7月開始用HKBN BB1000 24個月 $238嘅Plan<br />\n然後11月嗰陣有條HKBN友打嚟話送LeTV比我<br />\n講到明係免費 同埋聲稱會「送」返條100Mbps嘅線比LeTV用<br />\n咁我衰戇鳩聽到話免費就好好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知裝完簽左張紙先發現原來嗰張紙係加100M副線嘅合約 24個月 $58 係因為我有條主線BB1000所以先有58蚊呢個優惠價<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦我唔肯定自己當時喺電話係咪聽漏聽錯定點<br />\n我都費撚事打上去問 當自己戇鳩每個月食多58蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題嚟啦 我今年7月條主線到期 我想唔用HKBN想Cut<br />\n點知原來如果我要Cut嘅話唔可以一次過喺七月cut晒兩條線（因為我副線係11月先到期）<br />\n條友同我講三個情況，三個情況我都會蝕到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n1. cut 主線BB1000，然後副線無左優惠價會變正價$218（左右）食8-11月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 唔Cut 主線到11月再一次過Cut晒，但7-11月主線無左合約價變正價$398 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 7月一次過Cut鳩晒兩條線，但我要比埋淨低副線嗰幾個月嘅錢（58X4）<br />\n<br />\n條友仲推薦我用第2個方法，我真係吓左一聲，第3個方法仲要係我最後屌多兩屌先肯講，成件事衰自己戇鳩唔睇清楚合約內容。當然我最後只可以用第3個方法，蝕最少，但都係送錢比佢地。<br />\n呢個Post除左想鬧自己戇鳩外，想提醒各位用緊／將會用HKBN嘅朋友唔好中呢個伏（雖然可能得我咁蠢先會中伏）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b23d7959ba6452beba5df9ebbdb794eb90ff954","tid":158670,"uid":91512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"635645c9e89afb7222e11258992a780a2d4e2d70","tid":158670,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"搬屋解決一切"},{"pid":"fa70247c421fd6fe546f812a9ef76e64883bd41d","tid":158670,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬屋解決一切</blockquote><br />\n 有錢搬我仲駛為呢幾百一千動氣咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e7043b315b1a675a313c72b08609a4f3cbb38f","tid":158670,"uid":91464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9781fd62ff9817d2949e0bf2d6652417e71641f0","tid":158670,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff93a94fa54bfe87be9cd18dc8f4ac13e919a6a3","tid":158670,"uid":91512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"994e79cd24d90ae1bcd2e97cb125af8481a9648c","tid":158670,"uid":91512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:34:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a6dfd821f6f52e2b8d7e0b6c3de8881dd1a125f","tid":158670,"uid":91512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"193c8d96f09f8adfe76dceefa36bf44f0c53e836","tid":158670,"uid":91512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"383ee516e2f321bfd1e5adeff3984d478e8860ef","tid":158670,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:56:49.000Z","msg":"賤過有線wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點cut 都係要賠錢"},{"pid":"4bea3469b0aa23de7e5aa4752522df7ef93bbca6","tid":158670,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:55:17.000Z","msg":"有無friend屋企係無hkbn覆蓋？轉名俾佢然後免費cut"},{"pid":"72228b4c6fb0768e0e3332e1e7bbd27c9c35aa8d",